title: Georgia O'Keeffe Playing Cards
description:
Georgia O'Keeffe was a visionary painter of nature and the New Mexican landscape, of New York skyscrapers and vast, meticulous flower studies. Enriching this celebration of a great American modernist are beautiful photographic portraits by her husband Alfred Stieglitz.

2.48 in. x 3.46 in. x 0.75 in.
